@plane z=5 label="Delivery"
# Completion & Handoff

**Estimated completion:** 2026-04-10  
**Care card enclosed:** dry clean, no steam on lapel face, cedar hanger minimum 4 cm

**Final press sequence:**
1. Seams open on sleeve board (damp cloth, no direct iron)
2. Canvas set with tailor's ham, 10 s light weight
3. Collar roll steamed and dried on stand, 12 h
4. Lapels: wooden clapper, three passes

**Provenance label:** sewn inside back neck, woven in house font —  
`LEIF & CO. · LONDON · MADE FOR M. OSEI · 2026`

